@startuml
!theme plain

participant Window
participant Document
participant "div Container" as Div
participant "button" as Button

== Phase 1: Capturing (top → target) ==
Window -> Document: capture phase
Document -> Div: capture phase
Div -> Button: capture phase

== Phase 2: Target Phase ==
Button -> Button: event.target = button\nevent fires on target

== Phase 3: Bubbling (target → top) ==
Button -> Div: bubble phase
Div -> Document: bubble phase
Document -> Window: bubble phase

note over Window, Button
  Most listeners use bubble phase (default)
  Use { capture: true } to listen in capture phase
end note

@enduml
